{"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"@discardableResult","kind":"attribute"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"onNotifyNameOwner","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"text":"flags","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ConnectFlagsV","text":"ConnectFlags"},{"text":" = ConnectFlags(0), ","kind":"text"},{"text":"handler","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"@escaping"},{"text":" (","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO26DBusObjectManagerClientRefV","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"DBusObjectManagerClientRef","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusObjectManagerClientRef"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"ParamSpecRef","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ParamSpecRefV"},{"kind":"text","text":") -> "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:s4Voida","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Void"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","text":"Int"}],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Flags"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"flags"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The signal handler to call"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Run the given callback whenever the ","type":"text"},{"code":"notifyNameOwner","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" signal is emitted","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"handler"}]},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","text":"Discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Note that getting this signal doesn’t itself guarantee that the value of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the property has actually changed. When it is emitted is determined by the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"derived GObject class. If the implementor did not create the property with"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"[explicit_notify](\/\/documentation\/gobject\/explicit_notify, then any call to ","type":"text"},{"code":"g_object_set_property()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" results"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"in "},{"code":"notify","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" being emitted, even if the new value is the same as the old."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"If they did pass [explicit_notify](\/\/documentation\/gobject\/explicit_notify, then this signal is emitted only","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"when they explicitly call ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_notify()"},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_notify_by_pspec()"},{"type":"text","text":","},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and common practice is to do that only when the value has actually changed."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This signal is typically used to obtain change notification for a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"single property, by specifying the property name as a detail in the","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_signal_connect()"},{"type":"text","text":" call, like this:"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"(C Language Example):","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","code":["g_signal_connect (text_view->buffer, \"notify::paste-target-list\",","                  G_CALLBACK (gtk_text_view_target_list_notify),","                  text_view)"],"syntax":"C"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"It is important to note that you must use","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"#class@GObject.ParamSpec#parameter-names","isActive":true},{"text":" as","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"detail strings for the notify signal.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"aside","style":"note","name":"Note","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This represents the underlying "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"notify::name-owner"},{"type":"text","text":" signal"}]}]}],"kind":"content"}],"metadata":{"fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"onNotifyNameOwner"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"text":"flags","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ConnectFlagsV","text":"ConnectFlags"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"handler"},{"text":": (","kind":"text"},{"text":"DBusObjectManagerClientRef","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO26DBusObjectManagerClientRefV"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"text":"ParamSpecRef","preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ParamSpecRefV","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Void","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:s4Voida"},{"kind":"text","text":") -> "},{"text":"Int","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si"}],"externalID":"s:3GIO31DBusObjectManagerClientProtocolPAAE17onNotifyNameOwner5flags7handlerSi04GLibC012ConnectFlagsV_yAA0bcdE3RefV_AG09ParamSpecP0VtctF","roleHeading":"Instance Method","modules":[{"name":"GIO"}],"symbolKind":"method","extendedModule":"GIO","role":"symbol","title":"onNotifyNameOwner(flags:handler:)"},"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusObjectManagerClientProtocol"]]},"sections":[],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/gio\/dbusobjectmanagerclientprotocol\/onnotifynameowner(flags:handler:)"]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusObjectManagerClientProtocol\/onNotifyNameOwner(flags:handler: